# Use the Colab notebook (recommended)
Open `parallel-recognition/notebooks/parallel_recognition_colab.ipynb` in Colab and run cells in order.

# Quick CLI steps (alternative)
!git clone https://github.com/your_user/parallel-recognition.git
%cd parallel-recognition
!pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run image example
!python SRC/train_image_tpu.py --batch_size=512 --epochs=5

# Run speech example
!python SRC/train_speech_tpu.py --batch_size=128 --epochs=10

# Notes
- In Colab select `Runtime -> Change runtime type -> TPU` to use a TPU.
- Mount Google Drive to save checkpoints or data.
